OL,3,CJersey charities use art workshops to
OL,4,Chelp residents plan for future care
OL,6,FCare and local have come together for
OL,7,Fa new initiative which helps residents
OL,8,Fplan for their future care and support.
OL,10,FThe project, called 'Non Barriers
OL,11,FHere', uses arts-based methods, such
OL,12,Fas drawing and loom-making, to
OL,13,Fencourage conversations about things
OL,14,Flike medical treatments, funeral
OL,15,Farrangements and how they'd like to be
OL,16,Fremembered.
OL,18,FBy using colour, texture and
OL,19,Fsymbolism, residents can make their
OL,20,Fpersonal wishes known and recorded.
