OL,3,CJersey charities use art workshops to
OL,4,Chelp residents plan for future care
OL,6,FGail Edwards is Hospice Care Nurse
OL,7,FChampion and says conversations like
OL,8,Fthese are important: "We plan our
OL,9,Fholidays, we plan our finances, we
OL,10,Fplan what we'll do over the weekend
OL,11,Fbut this is a scary subject so we stay
OL,12,Faway from it.
OL,14,F"It doesn't matter where we are,
OL,15,Fwhether we're in good health, poor
OL,16,Fhealth, whether we have a learning
OL,17,Fdisability, whether we've got a
OL,18,Fterminal illness - it doesn't matter -
OL,19,Fwe should all be thinking about it and
OL,20,Frecording it."
