OL,3,CJersey charities use art workshops to
OL,4,Chelp residents plan for future care
OL,6,FThe project started in Stourbridge in
OL,7,Fthe UK during the Covid-19 pandemic
OL,8,Fand, if successful in Jersey, more
OL,9,Fworkshops will take place throughout
OL,10,Fthe year at Les Amis.
OL,12,FAlison Brolly is Les Amis' Registered
OL,13,FManager and says the project is
OL,14,Fproving popular: "For our residents,
OL,15,Fwho have a range of care needs, the
OL,16,Fworkshops empower them to talk about
OL,17,Fand understand a challenging topic, so
OL,18,Fthey can make important decisions
OL,19,Fabout their own care.
